          </tr>
          <tr class="alt">
            <td class="country-name"><a href="/en/countries/portugal/">Portugal</a></td>
            <td class="figure positive">17.5% of social security revenue</td>
            <td>AIMA (Agency for Integration, Migration and Asylum)</td>
            <td>Immigrants' share of total social security contributions (~€2.2bn). Zero-immigration scenario: fiscal burden rises by ~2.8pp of GDP</td>
            <td>2024</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="country-name"><a href="/en/countries/czechia/">Czechia</a></td>
            <td class="figure mixed">Ukraine TPS only: revenue CZK 8.2bn vs. expenditure CZK 3.9bn (quarterly)</td>
